## Deliverable — **Sound Brief** (copy-paste; you always fill every field)

```yaml
event_id: sfx_<context>_<move>_<tier>_##
use_case: <player hit enemy | bag | UI | footstep>
gameplay_moment: <frame sync: on hit-stop start | on active frame peak>
duration_ms: <e.g. 80–220 one-shot>
layers:
  transient:
    character: <click/slap/whip, bright, 2–8kHz energy>
    notes: <mono, dry>
  body:
    character: <thud/thump, mid-weight, 120–400Hz fundamental>
    notes: <short decay <150ms for light>
  sweetener:
    character: <whoosh / sub drop / debris>
    notes: <stereo width 0–60%>
spatial: 2D pan by camera relative OR centered (state)
reverb_send: <none | small room dojo | large>
variation: pitch_cents: [-120,0,120]; alternates_count: 3
mix_bus: SFX_Combat | SFX_UI | Music
polyphony: 1 | 3 | voice_steal_oldest
priority: high | medium | low
references_words: <5 adjectives, e.g. crunchy, dry, martial, snappy, close-mic>
anti_patterns: <no long reverb tail on chain hits; no white noise burst>
implementation_note: <Web Audio: which buffer pool; preload on title>
```

## Deliverable — **AI SFX generation prompt** (when user wants synthesized SFX)

Write **one paragraph** + **negative constraints**:

```text
Generate a short game SFX: single clean punch impact, close perspective, dry studio, sharp transient followed by tight low-mid thump 120Hz, minimal reverb, mono, 0.2 seconds, stylized brawler not realistic gore, no ambience, no music, no voice, no metallic ring
Negative: reverb tail >300ms, explosion, gun, orchestral, crowd, wind
```

For **kicks**, emphasize **swish → thump**; for **bag**, add **low boing** + **cloth**.

## Working with a non-expert user

Ask only: (1) **cartoon vs gritty**? (2) **blood tier** on or off (`[N]` §6.3.4)? (3) **Reference clip** URL?

Otherwise **ship the brief + 2 mix variants** (dry / juicy filenames).

## Anti-patterns

- One-shots that are **stereo wide** — wastes space and masks pan logic.
- **Uncompressed** WAV for every UI tick.
- Music with **full-spectrum** pads under combat with **no ducking**.
